《'''Hope There's Someone'''》是{{tsl|en|Antony and the Johnsons||Antony and the Johnsons}}演唱的歌曲，通过{{tsl|en|Rough Trade Records||Rough Trade}}和{{tsl|en|Secretly Canadian||Secretly Canadian}}发行于2005年6月7日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.secretlycanadian.com/onesheet.php?cat=SC114 |title=Antony and the Johnsons - Hope There's Someone |publisher=Secretly Canadian |accessdate=2012-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415033601/http://www.secretlycanadian.com/onesheet.php?cat=SC114 |archive-date=2012-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。这首歌是Antony and the Johnsons第二张录音室专辑《{{tsl|en|I Am a Bird Now||I Am a Bird Now}}》的主打单曲，也被认为是他们的标志性歌曲之一。2011年10月，《[[新音乐快递|新音乐快递]]》（''NME''）将这首曲子排在“过去15年150首最佳曲目”排行榜的第134位<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/list/150-best-tracks-of-the-past-15-years/248648/page/2 |title=150 Best Tracks Of The Past 15 Years |publisher=NME |date= |accessdate=2012-02-22 |archive-date=2015-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629013747/http://www.nme.com/list/150-best-tracks-of-the-past-15-years/248648/page/2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]]》将其评为21世纪第28首最佳歌曲<ref>{{cite web |title=The 200 Best Songs of the 2000s |url=https://pitchfork.com/features/lists-and-guides/7693-the-top-500-tracks-of-the-2000s-20-1/?page=10 |website=Pitchfork |publisher=Pitchfork Media Group |accessdate=2019-01-24 |archive-date=2018-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622032613/https://pitchfork.com/features/lists-and-guides/7693-the-top-500-tracks-of-the-2000s-20-1/?page=10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

封面图是乔伊·加布里埃尔（Joey Gabriel）的视频中的图片。

截至2016年3月，《Hope There's Someone》在英国已售出50568张<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.musicweek.com/businessanalysis/read/official-charts-analysis-the-1975-top-the-official-album-chart/064253|title=Official Charts Analysis: The 1975 top the Official Albums Chart|last=Jones|first=Alan|date=2016-03-04|work={{tsl|en|Music Week||Music Week}}|publisher=Intent Media|accessdate=2016-03-04|subscription=yes }}</ref>。

